      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: this vehicle arrives in showroom-ready condition, reflecting a level of care that is rarely seen on the secondary market. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been meticulously preserved to meet the highest standards of automotive excellence. This is a collector-grade example offering an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. Fully inspected and ready for immediate delivery.",
