    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a world where time slows down and every drive feels like a scene from a classic film. This Midnight Sapphire grand tourer is more than a vehicle; it is a preserved piece of automotive history. The interior, draped in supple, cream-colored hides, still carries the faint, nostalgic scent of expensive leather and polished wood. When the engine breathes to life, it does so with a whisper of power that suggests limitless potential, while the bodywork gleams with a luster so deep you could lose yourself in its reflection. This is a rare opportunity to possess a soul-stirring machine that looks and feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor in a dream you never wanted to end.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
